{"tid":2155947,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"他願以生命相報 - 蔣芸","createTime":"2020-08-14T06:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T06:18:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"80aa4d6e1064fed9aafca7ba7dfc31aebb179794","tid":2155947,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T06:18:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200724/FYBXPEM4MFHJTF7BSBJWO44Z2A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200724%2FFYBXPEM4MFHJTF7BSBJWO44Z2A%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR1BOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=5f0d33ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200724%2FFYBXPEM4MFHJTF7BSBJWO44Z2A%2F&h=da030348\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200724/FYBXPEM4MFHJTF7BSBJWO44Z2A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n他願以生命相報 - 蔣芸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XfC-PhBqogSxWk6cHVJvjVOCM7U=/5369x3729/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DZNA322GBRDITDGCCYMIJ6JYSU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FXfC-PhBqogSxWk6cHVJvjVOCM7U%3D%2F5369x3729%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDZNA322GBRDITDGCCYMIJ6JYSU.JPG&h=fd592ca6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豈有不知在此時此。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n但是，香港人的特質在多次考驗中早已被領教了；不平則鳴，不平則走出來，雖然如今已不可能，但他們仍然用自己的方式來表達對眼前所發生的一切大大不滿；可憐的復可敬的人們啊！<br />\n<br />\n唯一一份足可代表香港仍然有言論自由的媒體就要淪陷了；人們說即使明天只出一張白紙，仍然要撐落去，一句話能立刻叫人愴然下淚。人們用有限的籌碼護盤，讓在多方折騰之下快要保不住的江山一剎那間有了起色，一個個本是平凡、平凡而有感，心中還有一把尺，更有良知的呼喚；。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。多年來在風雨飄搖的海上，一葉孤舟黑夜航行幾回要被吞噬沒頂，但他挺到了今天，他並不孤單，不斷有隱約的喝采聲與吶喊聲傳來&hellip;&hellip;鼓舞着他，他說過兩手空空來到這個城市，只因為曾享有自由而有所得，如今願以生命相報也在所不惜。"}]}